    {
      "name": "WW2 Fighter (Allied, Late-War)",
      "size": 7,
      "loco": "turboprop",
      "desc": "Long-range escort fighter. Mustangs, Thunderbolts, and Tempests \u2014 six-plus guns and the legs to use them.",
      "notes": "P-51 Mustangs in all their marks, P-47 Thunderbolts, Hawker Tempests, Lavochkin La-7s, and Yakovlev Yak-3s. The late-war Allied fighters that turned air superiority from a contest into a foregone conclusion. The Mustang's combination of range, speed, and firepower made her the complete package \u2014 escort bombers to Berlin and back, dogfight anything the Luftwaffe sent up, strafe ground targets on the return leg. Six or more guns and the fuel to use them.",
      "toughLevel": 0,
      "armourLevel": -1,
      "speedLevel": 0,
      "handlingLevel": 1,
      "mods": {},
