    {
      "name": "Modern Air Superiority Fighter",
      "size": 9,
      "loco": "jet",
      "desc": "Twin-engine, Mach 2.5, designed to own the sky. Eagles, Flankers, Typhoons, and Rafales.",
      "notes": "F-15 Eagles, F-22 Raptors, Eurofighter Typhoons, Dassault Rafales, Saab Gripens, and their equivalents. Twin-engine, Mach 2+ capable, designed to own the sky from visual range to beyond-visual-range. The F-15 has never been shot down in air-to-air combat. The F-22 was built to ensure that record continues. She's the thing your players hear about but never want to see on the wrong side. Night Vision.",
